Class AbstOrganism

java.lang.Object
  greenfoot.Actor
      AbstOrganism

public abstract class AbstOrganism
extends greenfoot.Actor

AbstOrganism is the base class for all organism operations. Has functionality to feed, grow, clone, kill, move and mutate an organism. This is Mr. Rowbottom's version for us to use Needs lots of clean up
